title: HypeerX Gaming house TSM #1

embed.description: What is home life like for the TSM boys? Join Doublelift and Biofrost as they take you on an exclusive tour of the Team SoloMid LoL Gaming House! Do you want to see more House Tours like this? Be sure to subscribe to our channel so you'll never miss a video!

body: Navigando sulle notizie di Reddit sono capitato su un video che mostra la House gaming che ospita i TSM, dura solo 5 mminti e mostra come vivono i proplayer, se siete curiosi buona visione {{item:3340}}
